main event: A disc-shaped object clipped from a magazine was reported as a UFO sighting in Indianapolis, Indiana on February 7, 1951.
interesting points: The sighting was reported to Project Blue Book, the official U.S. Air Force program that investigated UFO sightings.
The report card indicates that a photograph was taken, but it is not included in the image provided.
The report card lists various other UFO sightings and observations from March through July 1951 across different locations in the United States.
Some of the sightings were evaluated as being caused by natural phenomena like meteors or flares, while others were listed as 'unidentified'.
The document suggests that the U.S. Air Force was actively investigating and documenting UFO sightings during this time period.
